<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Summary">Summary</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="https://wiki.socr.umich.edu/index.php/File:SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="./heights_1_files/150px-SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg" width="150" height="153" class="thumbimage" srcset="/images/thumb/a/ae/SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg/225px-SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg 1.5x, /images/a/ae/SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg 2x"></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="https://wiki.socr.umich.edu/index.php/File:SOCR_Data_Dinov_HeightWeight_062408_Fig1.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_height">Human Height and Weight</a></div></div></div>
<p>Human <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_height">Height</a> and <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_weight">Weight</a> are mostly hereditable, but lifestyles (e.g., regular strenuous physical exercise), diet, health and environmental factors also play a role in determining individual's physical characteristics. The dataset below contains 1035 records of heights and weights for some current and recent <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mlb.mlb.com/index.jsp">Major League Baseball (MLB)</a> Players. These data were obtained from different resources (e.g., <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www-958.ibm.com/software/data/cognos/manyeyes/datasets?q=MLB">IBM Many Eyes</a> and the <a href="https://wiki.socr.umich.edu/index.php/SOCR_Data_MLB_HeightsWeights#References" title="SOCR Data MLB HeightsWeights">references below</a>). See also the <a href="https://wiki.socr.umich.edu/index.php/SOCR_Data_Dinov_020108_HeightsWeights" title="SOCR Data Dinov 020108 HeightsWeights"> 25,000 records of adolescent height and weight</a>.
</p><p>The data includes the following variables:
</p>
<ul><li><b>Name</b>: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mlb.mlb.com/index.jsp">MLB</a> Player Name</li>
<li><b>Team</b>: The <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mlb.mlb.com/team/">Baseball team</a> the player was a member of at the time the data was acquired</li>
<li><b>Position</b>: Player <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baseball_field">field position</a></li>
<li><b>Height(inches)</b>: Player height in inches</li>
<li><b>Weight(pounds)</b>: Player weight in pounds</li>
<li><b>Age</b>: Player age at time of record</li></ul>
